quote_text:
```json
{
  "evidence_quotes": {
    "tribal_dominance": [
      "why America is the greatest country ever to exist, or why free markets are the most moral, proven and effective economic system ever discovered, or why the Constitution is the greatest political document ever written",
      "They have always hated this country."
    ],
    "individual_dignity": [
      "So I see a conservative movement that will stand for the dignity of all people, unborn, pre-born, newly born, all people."
    ],
    "fear": [
      "the left has done everything they possibly can to make sure our generation has never heard why America is the greatest country ever to exist",
      "the fight that I've decided to engage in is one that will either make or break Western civilization."
    ],
    "hope": [
      "If there is one thing we take away from what this president has taught us, is that when we as a movement fight, we win.",
      "It will be the most important culture war in American history, and we will win."
    ],
    "envy": [
      "If you want to get love from the left, be a conservative that attacks Donald Trump. If you want to get on the mainstream networks, be a conservative that writes poorly about this president.",
      "But if you want to be loved, you want to get invited to the cocktail parties, you want to get all the right compliments on Twitter, then sure, attack the president."
    ],
    "mudita": [
      "She's done more to move the black community to conservative values in the last year than I think anyone does in the last 30 years. So God bless you, Candace, for what you've done. Totally amazing.",
      "Folks, we have that president and he is fighting for us every single day."
    ],
    "enmity": [
      "They have always hated this country. They have always had contempt for our history.",
      "I'm so sick and tired of saying that the Democrat Party and liberals mean well. They do not mean well."
    ],
    "amity": [
      "You must understand those of us that decide to stand and defend this president, it can be very tough."
    ],
    "fragmentative_goals": [
      "I don't want to live in the country that the socialist left wants to create. We are not going in the same direction as the Democrat Party. [...] We do not have different ways of getting to the same place. We have two different places that we want to get to.",
      "Is America a place for victims or for victors? Is America a place where you can achieve your dreams or dwell in mediocrity? Is America a socialist place or is America a place that embraces freedom and is a refuge for those that have fled totalitarian Marxist dictatorships? That will be the question of the 2020 election."
    ],
    "cohesive_goals": [
      "We must do what is right. Do what is correct and stand for truth.",
      "That's the conservative movement that I see."
    ]
  }
}
```

